sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as PackageLinked
    participant FS as FileSystem
    participant Composer

    User->>CLI: orbit package linked app
    CLI->>CLI: Build app path from ~/projects/
    
    CLI->>FS: Check appPath exists
    alt App not found
        FS-->>CLI: false
        CLI-->>User: Error - App not found
    else App exists
        FS-->>CLI: true
        CLI->>Composer: composer linked
        Note over Composer: Run in appPath directory
        Composer-->>CLI: output lines
        
        CLI->>CLI: Parse output format
        Note over CLI: vendor/package -> /path/to/source
        CLI->>CLI: Extract name and path pairs
        
        alt No linked packages
            CLI-->>User: No linked packages for app
        else Has linked packages
            CLI-->>User: List of packages with paths
        end
    end
